等, 等完又入唔到, 入唔到又再等<br />\n<br />\n架爆𨋢入面d人又on99睇住你停1樓𨋢又入唔到, 大家都哂左時間<br />\n<br />\n其他時間唔講, 但繁忙時間真係冇乜理由要搭𨋢"},{"pid":"cb89ba60d5f554824b2f0db51304ee96ad02888c","tid":894374,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d7d74fc2b35aa15e358aa17f273bf8da0d53936","tid":894374,"uid":124613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"換個角度，<br />\n如果係你住一樓呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"比我緊係行樓梯"},{"pid":"3ce842c2a2fdc37cb989d9fb8c986b51dedc2c93","tid":894374,"uid":137582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T16:50:45.000Z","msg":"通常撞到樓主呢種人，我都會行返出lift hold 住然後叫佢出黎行樓梯，反正到左1樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f758612042ce470620183e155584b11c9bcfc5","tid":894374,"uid":166820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"睇下係咪老人家囉，老人家行一條路梯都死得架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc913d1a79ab245121e245d0e2953461560b9ea","tid":894374,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 住一樓要落樓，我會照㩒𨋢之後行樓梯</span>"},{"pid":"6a66cb48cd3eb09cdaf14cd711faf16d5052c72d","tid":894374,"uid":39128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T17:36:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得樓豬可能激動咗但我好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時朝早番學 架𨋢已經好爆 去到一/二樓<br />\n啲人仲想逼入黎 逼唔到又再等<br />\n其實你咁physically able 逼入黎<br />\n不如行一兩層落平台搭啦<br />\n仲要有時某啲𨋢唔會直落地下其實你都係去平台姐..<br />\n番工都趕時間啦仲特登等咁耐𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51907a00b3a08f1a9a0633ae8eb8528e656494f","tid":894374,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a66cb48cd3eb09cdaf14cd711faf16d5052c72d","tid":894374,"uid":39128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T17:36:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得樓豬可能激動咗但我好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時朝早番學 架𨋢已經好爆 去到一/二樓<br />\n啲人仲想逼入黎 逼唔到又再等<br />\n其實你咁physically able 逼入黎<br />\n不如行一兩層落平台搭啦<br />\n仲要有時某啲𨋢唔會直落地下其實你都係去平台姐..<br />\n番工都趕時間啦仲特登等咁耐𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T17:41:21.000Z","msg":"靚女或後生OL逼入黎冇所謂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a847a6dfec39960e0a0bf41233132f29e6fe8f","tid":894374,"uid":19172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"有次有個男人係我出左去果時，就黎閂門果時鬧我<br />\n<br />\n我立即轉身禁開門制再屌鳩佢"},{"pid":"8b61da6a020fcb8093e593627b8e38f2f4ad6b46","tid":894374,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"吹啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔鋸咪搬囉"},{"pid":"575060721e1521bfdb1584aa628a4aa26c43135f","tid":894374,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7be5f1fe488104d0d883af72aee126b02e22ae43","tid":894374,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"住2樓都係 正垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T18:01:36.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1-5樓啲人都係垃圾"},{"pid":"4bb1fc9004ead78fcc705f260429af2a41e020f3","tid":894374,"uid":73546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T18:05:17.000Z","msg":"住一樓 行到落樓架𨋢都未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa3b35cde4b31ac1043d73d902a1ead5235cf13","tid":894374,"uid":44477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T18:12:19.000Z","msg":"住高層個d落樓個陣唔好搭lift啦，上到最頂先落番落，晒時間，行落黎啦。<br />\n照樓豬個67思維，尖沙咀去金鐘搭地鐵個班人，游水得啦，一個站，唔好阻人去柴灣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733c4cbf486c8e7a1beb8da99271187ec18d308d","tid":894374,"uid":30829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T18:59:45.000Z","msg":"傻閪人地想搭咪搭 關你撚事<br />\n究竟現實中有幾廢柴先要上黎刷存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4bdf332e22c256804a5013359eea81a4ac74de","tid":894374,"uid":177924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T22:47:39.000Z","msg":"之前做完大手術攞住兩枝拐杖同屋企人搭lift上一樓<br />\n好多人搭同一部<br />\n有個典型閪港嬸見到一樓有人禁即刻摺出聲講左句住一樓就行樓梯啦<br />\n到左一樓我一行出去睥左佢一眼<br />\n佢見到我兩枝拐杖先細細聲講 哦原來用拐杖既<br />\n同lift啲人都笑住望佢<br />\n我就話果刻有兩枝野可以話到俾人知我有需要搭啫<br />\n但如果我係肚痛頭暈病<br />\n係咪要同你解釋左先可以搭啊<br />\n更何況根本就無呢個需要<br />\n屌你咁撚霸道就去住村屋啦<br />\n我都明返工時間搭lift落樓滿左人停一樓係好無謂亦都哂時間<br />\n所以我平時落樓都係行樓梯<br />\n但你有交租我又有交租<br />\n我係平常時間排隊搭lift上一樓都得罪你喎<br />\n通常呢啲摺摺聲既都係啲自私到仆街既廢老同垃圾"},{"pid":"457e776d270afd6f5f919e1cc80d93d357cba4b6","tid":894374,"uid":177924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T22:50:41.000Z","msg":"真係好撚on9<br />\n樓主仲要特登開個post黎同大家講自己係幾撚自私<br />\n仲要話好撚抵屌<br />\n你就好撚抵屌啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}